data.description:
PC3181. ONE QUARTER acre at the END of CUL-DE-SAC. Backs into a true green belt, & 5 minute walk to Converse park. Has lake stocked with fish! 2 miles from Randolph, 3 miles I-10. Community POOL, with park. Lots of families and military here. GRANITE dining room table and other BIG furniture is negotiable. Sellers are downsizing. TWO living areas down stairs. Peaceful kitchen bay window to sit with coffee and enjoy the view !! Lot big enough for pool, and huge parties. Monster master and bath!!!

Brokered And Advertised By: Coldwell Banker D'Ann Harper
Listing Agent: Vincent Reilly
